Project Modules

This project has declared the following modules:

Name Description
Doclet A custom doclet that is used to generate site documentation for configuration classes.
Soy Juice A guice module that makes it easy to render Soy templates compiled by closure-maven-plugin from Java code.
Closure Maven Plugin A plugin that eases web application building by integrating Closure Compiler (JS), Closure Templates, Closure StyleSheets, and Protocol Buffers.
